(147, 5, 'Affordable 4 BHK Apartments Starting at Just $199/Month', '4-bhk-apartments-at-just-dollar-199-monthly-rent', 'Finding a spacious and affordable home in a prime location might sound like a dream, but it doesn’t have to be. Living in a modern, 4 BHK apartment for just $199 a month is now a reality. These units offer the perfect balance of space, convenience, and value, making them ideal for families, roommates, or anyone looking to upgrade their living situation without breaking the bank.', 'With limited availability, now is your chance to snag one of these incredible offers and start enjoying a better lifestyle, all while staying within your budget. But act fast because opportunities like this don’t stick around for long!', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/147_ZWaQzbfj_.jpg?updatedAt=1733128205174', 2, 'Affordable 4 BHK Apartments for $199/Month | Prime Location', 'Spacious 4 BHK apartments are now available for just $199/month. They offer modern amenities and a prime location. Secure your dream home now! ', '4 BHK Apartment', 6, '2024-12-02', '2024-12-02 07:25:05'),
(148, 3, 'The Role of Private Adult Daycare Caregivers in Our Society', 'vital-role-of-private-adult-daycare-caregivers', 'Caring for our aging population is one of society’s most important responsibilities, and at the heart of it are private adult daycare caregivers. These talented and compassionate individuals provide personalized care and support to elderly individuals, allowing them to lead safe, dignified, and emotionally fulfilling lives. ', 'Their efforts benefit seniors, bring peace of mind to families, and play a critical role in the healthcare ecosystem. This blog highlights the invaluable contributions of private adult daycare caregivers and explores how their contribution matters to our society.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/148_wTGsQVoEVx.jpg?updatedAt=1733211340194', 3, 'The Vital Role of Private Adult Daycare Caregivers', 'Understand the vital role of private adult daycare caregivers in supporting elderly independence, safety, and well-being with personalized care and attention.', 'Private Adult Daycare Caregivers ', 7, '2024-12-03', '2024-12-03 05:47:19');
