(60, 4, 'Boost Your Real Estate Business with Innovative Strategies', 'real-estate-business', 'Innovation is crucial in the constantly changing world of real estate. Two revolutionary solutions, Customer Management Software (CMS) and Prefabricated Buildings, are catching everyone\'s eye. These technologies aren\'t just making waves but modifying the entire industry, resulting in improved efficiency, sustainability, and customer satisfaction.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/60_gEHvjonzM.jpg?updatedAt=1713788396388', 3, 'The Ultimate Guide to Modernizing Your Real Estate Business', 'Learn how to integrate Customer Management Software and Prefabricated Buildings to streamline operations for a greener future in real estate.', 'real estate business, integrate Customer Management Software, Prefabricated Buildings,  greener future in real estate', 2, '2024-04-21', '2024-04-22 08:23:56'),
(61, 5, 'Discounted SUVs: Dealerships Clearing Out Unsold Inventory', 'big-discounts-on-unsold-suvs', 'Amidst a notable shift in the automotive market, dealerships are slashing prices on various SUV models that await their first drive. An interplay of factors, from evolving consumer preferences to economic shifts, has sparked these unprecedented discounts spanning midsize, compact, luxury, and electric SUVs.', 'Join us as we delve into this trend and unravel strategies to leverage these outstanding deals.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/61_Q2j19zPfR.jpg?updatedAt=1714049983681', 2, 'Get Big Discounts on Unsold SUVs at Dealerships in 2024', 'Explore enticing discounts on remaining SUVs at dealerships! Benefit from our expert advice to save considerably and drive away in your dream vehicle.', 'suvs', 1, '2024-04-25', '2024-04-25 13:00:36'),
(62, 5, 'A Guide to Stairlift Installation: Everything You Need to Know', 'guide-to-stairlift-installation', 'Stairlifts can be the ultimate solution for those facing mobility challenges, allowing them to access all floors safely. But naturally, the installation process can raise questions.', 'This guide addresses all your concerns. It will give you an in-depth insight into how to install stairlifts, address your concerns about home damage, and equip you with the knowledge to confidently embark on a journey towards a more accessible and independent living space.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/62__qc2WfjVr_.jpg?updatedAt=1714049979153', 3, 'How to Install a Stairlift At Home? | Process, Damage & More', 'A stairlift can be the ultimate solution for those seeking mobility assistance at home. But how do we install it, and does it cause damage? Read on to find out.', 'Stairlift', 2, '2024-04-25', '2024-04-25 13:04:07'),
(63, 5, 'Senior Living Communities & Strategies for Saving Money', 'affordable-senior-living-communities', 'Senior living communities are thoughtfully made to meet the varied needs of older adults, providing many services, amenities, and care options. The diverse choices can elicit both anticipation and apprehension for seniors and their caregivers as they transition into senior living.', 'Finding the ideal community that fits your lifestyle, needs, and budget requires thoroughly understanding each option\'s characteristics. Explore a range of senior living communities here and discover cost-effective strategies for smoothly transitioning into this new phase of life.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/63_gW3G546P7W.jpg?updatedAt=1714049980067', 2, 'A Guide to Affordable Senior Living Communities', 'Explore the nuances of selecting the ideal senior living community tailored to your budget and lifestyle. Prepare for a worry-free retirement starting today!', 'living community', 3, '2024-04-25', '2024-04-25 13:05:45'),
(64, 3, 'The Ultimate Guide to Full-Mouth Dental Implants: Benefits and Costs', 'full-mouth-dental-implants-guide', 'The correlation between oral health and general well-being is undeniable, making exploring dental treatments and innovations a critical aspect of health discourse. Full-mouth dental implants stand out as a premier solution for individuals aiming to restore their smiles fully.', 'This segment will explore the financial considerations of this dental procedure and discuss its extensive benefits.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/64_4ybt3dmRW.jpg?updatedAt=1714049976364', 3, 'Full Mouth Dental Implants: Costs, Benefits and More!', 'Discover full-mouth dental implants, their costs, and the life-changing benefits of complete dental restoration.', 'Dental Implants', 4, '2024-04-25', '2024-04-25 13:12:07'),
